Summary: Did not observe until photo was uploaded to computer.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my front yard taking pictures of the Moon and Venus and Jupiter. Did not observe the phenomena until picture was uploaded to my laptop. The picture of the object appeared in only one of my photographs. All of the photographs were taken with in a few minutes of each other. Does not appear to be moving. I guess it could have been a digital glitch, but have never had this happen. I was trying out a new camera with a very strong telephoto lens.
